00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:41.000
even though the data is being updated to a separate environment.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:44.000
So these reports themselves, kind of as a side effect,

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:48.000
are very beneficial in terms of I can go look at the different pieces

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:51.000
and kind of make sure that things are going as expected,

