Another benefit of Connect in terms of more from the admin perspective

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:03.000
is if I go in here to the admin panel and look at scheduled content,

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:07.000
I can see all the different things that have been scheduled for my entire team.

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:12.000
So you can see there's a lot of stuff that we've scheduled here for our demo server,

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:14.000
and some of these are very common.

