and some of them are occurring maybe once a day or a few times a day.

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:23.000
So I get this nice little snapshot and be like,

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.000
hey, maybe I don't want to have this be running every single minute.

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:29.000
I can go check on that, view the content,

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:31.000
and make sure I actually want it to be executing,

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:33.000
as well as the timeframes it's executing,

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:37.000
making sure things are overlaying and that we have everything going nicely.

