or a collection of datasets that you're storing.

00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:24.000
There's native connectors to things like AWS S3

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:28.000
or Azure AD, Azure Data Lake Service,

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:31.000
as well as Google Cloud, Kaggle,

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:33.000
and a few different other locations.

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:36.000
So I can just call a board register RStudio Connect.

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:39.000
It's going to automatically read in my R environment

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:42.000
for the URL and my credentials.

